# <%= appName %> — Clean Architecture

Dependencies point **inward**. The domain knows nothing about frameworks, databases, or HTTP.

## Layers

| Layer | Path | Depends on |
|-------|------|------------|
| Domain | `src/domain/` | Nothing |
| Application | `src/application/` | Domain |
| Infrastructure | `src/infrastructure/` | Domain, Application (ports) |
| Presentation | `src/presentation/` | Application |

## Dependency rule

```
Presentation → Application → Domain
Infrastructure → Domain (implements ports)
```

## Commands

```bash
my make module <name>   # prefer placing use cases in src/application/use-cases/
```

Use `src/composition-root.ts` to wire concrete adapters to interfaces.
